{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all became very, very, you know, close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But while we were in these camps-- well, in this [POLISH], [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] it comes to my mind, we all of a sudden, we, we start building a cement factory, next to the camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I became head engineer, to help the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was able to always try to figure out things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so there were a lot of people who could not even handle a screw or a screwdriver.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was able to manage to adapt myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was sort of helping the youngsters or even elderly people who were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we were able to continue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, kosher was a problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you didn't eat no meat, but still, the rest of the food, it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were still-- we organized a synagogue in the concentration camp-- in this camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were able to it came the holidays, we were still able to-- so the non-Jews, they brought us some flour on Pesach, I remember.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We baked matzos inside a oven, which we built for to make cement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But before the oven was workable, we baked inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We put a fire, we baked, baked matzos and we ate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [BACKGROUND NOISE] even at work, we were sometimes were working late at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you wouldn't go home-- go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You wouldn't go back to camp, until you finished your work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there it was, Pesach, even on Pesach night, at the Seder.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we just had our ration, whatever, at the time it was, a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as I remembered, I still, I still-- I remember some of the Haggadah by heart.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
